<HEADLINE>
<P>
PEROT ON NAFTA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Regarding Ross Perot's reported reluctance to concede defeat over the NAFTA 
issue (Sept. 11): 
</P>
<P>
 It appears the "giant trucking sound" going south that we now hear has not 
impacted the views of Perot or the membership of "United We Strand America 
Inc." Instead, we are again beseeched to open our ears to the now familiar 
"giant clucking sound" of our favorite banty rooster of populism. What has been 
most audible, however, is the "giant ducking sound" of a politician who seethes 
at the mouth when asked to provide a straightforward answer to a direct 
question. What say we start a Wake Up America movement, and settle things over 
a cup of coffee. 
</P>
<P>
 RUSSELL TRAVIS 
</P>
<P>
 Bakersfield 
</P>
