ninth-ranked Los Alamitos (5-1) with a 7-6, 6-1, 6-1 sweep at No.1 doubles. 
Laura Rubin swept at No. 1 singles, 6-3, 6-0, 6-0 for third-ranked Mater Dei 
(2-2). 
</P>
