The 73-year-old woman said the defendant broke into her apartment and came into 
her bedroom about 2:30 a.m., touched her and tried to kiss her. 
</P>
<P>
 Police said Stewart was still in the apartment building when they arrived. A 
Ventura County sheriff's detective testified that a drunken Stewart had been 
spotted at a local bowling alley several hours before the attacks on the women, 
and that he had been making advances at other women and offered one money to 
have sex with him. 
</P>
<P>
 Deputy Dist. Atty. Patrice D. Koenig said the victims did not want to have to 
testify at trial. DWAYNE BRAY 
