 Gun type: Raven MP25* 
</P>
<P>
 Guns traced: 287 
</P>
<P>
 Gun type: Davis P-380* 
</P>
<P>
 Guns traced: 260 
</P>
<P>
 Gun type: Stallard/Maverick JS9 
