 Source: Orange County Annual Survey, UCI Outlook for Business Is Upbeat 
</P>
<P>
 Optimism regarding the national economy has turned upward in Orange County. 
About half say business conditions will be good during the next year. Although 
residents are split on the longer term outlook, the current four in 10 who 
think good times will last is a significant increase from 1993. 
</P>
<P>
 Turning to business conditions in the country as a whole, do you think that 
during the next 12 months we will have good times financially or bad times? 
</P>
<P>
