during the next five years, or will we have periods of widespread unemployment 
or depression? 
</P>
<P>
 1994: 
</P>
<P>
 Good times: 43% 
</P>
<P>
 Bad times: 45% 
</P>
<P>
 Don't know: 12% 
</P>
<P>
 Percentage saying "good times": 
</P>
<P>
 1994: 43% 
</P>
<P>
 Source: Orange County Annual Survey, UCI 
</P>
